<div class="wrap">
<section id="products" class="reveal">
  <div class="s-head">
    <div class="s-tag" style="color:var(--sage)">CHOOSE YOUR PROTECTION</div>
    <h2 class="s-title">Two Products. One Mission.</h2>
    <p class="s-sub">Different filtration levels for different needs. Both designed for women navigating hormonal changes.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="prod-grid">
    <div class="prod-card" style="border:2px solid var(--bdr)">
      <div class="prod-img prod-img--sage"><div class="prod-ph" style="border:2px dashed rgba(94,138,106,.3);color:var(--sage);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;padding:24px"><span style="font-size:36px;opacity:.5">📸</span><span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;opacity:.7">2.0 Handheld</span><span style="font-size:14px;opacity:.4">Product photo with hose &amp; 3 spray modes · 600×400px</span></div></div>
      <div class="prod-body">
        <div class="prod-badges"><span class="badge badge--sage">BEST STARTER</span><span class="badge badge--muted">5-STAGE FILTER</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-size:26px;margin-bottom:10px">The 2.0 Handheld</h3>
        <p style="font-size:16px;color:var(--mut);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:18px">5-stage filtration with 3 spray modes and a flexible hose. Removes chlorine, chloramines, heavy metals, VOCs, and PFAS at a price that makes filtered water accessible.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:12px;margin-bottom:18px"><span class="prod-price">$49</span><span class="prod-was">$69</span><span class="badge badge--save">SAVE $20</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--sage)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--sage)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>5-stage filtration (Sediment → Calcium Sulfite → Vitamin C → KDF-55 → Catalytic Carbon)</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--sage)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--sage)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>3 spray modes: Rain, Massage, Jet</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--sage)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--sage)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>60″ flexible hose — reaches everywhere</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--sage)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--sage)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>Filter life: 3 months / 5,000 gallons</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--sage)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--sage)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>Replacement filters from $15/quarter</span></div>
        <button class="btn btn--sage" style="width:100%;margin-top:22px">Shop the 2.0 Handheld →</button>
        <p class="prod-best">Best for: Budget-friendly protection &amp; flexibility</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="prod-card" style="border:2px solid rgba(176,134,66,.5)">
      <div class="badge badge--popular" style="position:absolute;top:16px;right:16px;z-index:2;border-radius:16px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:14px">MOST POPULAR</div>
      <div class="prod-img prod-img--gold"><div class="prod-ph" style="border:2px dashed rgba(176,134,66,.4);color:var(--gold);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;padding:24px"><span style="font-size:36px;opacity:.5">📸</span><span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;opacity:.7">5.0 Stationary</span><span style="font-size:14px;opacity:.4">Wall-mount product photo with filter visible · 600×400px</span></div></div>
      <div class="prod-body">
        <div class="prod-badges"><span class="badge badge--gold">ADVANCED PROTECTION</span><span class="badge badge--muted">15-STAGE FILTER</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-size:26px;margin-bottom:10px">The 5.0 Stationary</h3>
        <p style="font-size:16px;color:var(--mut);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:18px">15-stage advanced filtration extends each stage with deeper media beds plus pH rebalancing, fluoride reduction, and mineral infusion. Infuses Vitamin C &amp; E. The gold standard for hormonal hair protection.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:12px;margin-bottom:18px"><span class="prod-price">$89</span><span class="prod-was">$119</span><span class="badge badge--save">SAVE $30</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--gold)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>15-stage deep filtration + Vitamin C/E infusion</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--gold)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>Wall-mount, high-pressure fixed head</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--gold)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>NSF/ANSI 177 certified</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--gold)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>Filter life: 6 months / 10,000 gallons</span></div>
        <div class="cr"><svg class="ci" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" fill="var(--gold)" opacity=".15"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>Replacement filters from $32/6 months</span></div>
        <button class="btn btn--gold" style="width:100%;margin-top:22px">Shop the 5.0 Stationary →</button>
        <p class="prod-best">Best for: Maximum protection for aging hair &amp; skin</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>

